{"tid":1030792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「紅了就不用上班賺錢」 28歲男拍片跳河不幸浸死","createTime":"2019-02-21T07:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T13:37:41.000Z","uid":75969,"like":399,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"6f59b144981a27937fee295236732fa570124ab3","tid":1030792,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190221/_2019022114015139199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190221%2F_2019022114015139199.jpg&h=7116c0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地一名28歲男子想靠直播賺錢，深信「紅了就不用上班賺錢」，為增加人氣竟然找網友替他拍跳河影片，最後不幸溺死。<br />\n<br />\n28歲的郝姓男子「快手」平台當主播，曾經因拍了一段小短片，賺了幾百元人民幣，令他決定要經營好直播平台。他深信「紅了就不用上班賺錢」。為了衝高粉絲人數，大年初五他找來網友幫手拍下自己在寒冷天氣下跳河的片段。他對鏡頭說：「今天我就給大家來點刺激的，提醒朋友們現在只有4度，我就在這裡給大家老鐵們拍個跳水的段子。」<br />\n<br />\n話一說完，郝男就縱身跳下河，但他遲遲沒有上來，在旁協助拍攝的網友察覺不對，立刻請途人一同到河中尋找，結果發現河水很淺，郝男頭部和臉部受傷，相信是因為河水太淺，導頭部受撞擊昏迷溺斃身亡，送去醫院搶救後不治​。<br />\n<br />\n該段跳河影片成了郝男的死亡直播，意外爆紅，但他卻不能親眼看到自己爆紅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/938509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F938509&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=21e85e39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F938509&h=4cb9cd57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/938509</a>"},{"pid":"02ff7bc0c3f25732cfea491e45cf8cbdf1c510a6","tid":1030792,"uid":39496,"like":276,"dislike":1,"score":275,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"求仁得仁"},{"pid":"c5feb4d7707298cebade57ba27eec0b27196812b","tid":1030792,"uid":50502,"like":568,"dislike":1,"score":567,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"死了就不用上班賺錢"},{"pid":"41d50acdac59c3bea0f85d65c2f3bcd8145dc50d","tid":1030792,"uid":75969,"like":618,"dislike":1,"s